    "text": "There has been considerable concern about the potential risks to privacy and open-source initiatives. Yet, most of it seems to come from new crypto tools. I don't think we do ourselves a favour by using crypto and all the related scams as the leading example for privacy and open-source. # opensource # crypto # privacy https://www. ainvest.com/news/legal-risks-c rypto-privacy-tools-future-open-source-innovation-2508/",
